对科学的时候，希望你能更严谨，更谦逊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有想法是好事，但是觉得别人是傻逼，不是一件好事。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563299740,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1f1a4f278ce4decc1a95d4d3fa069b78","url_token":"an-lian-de-yijiao-31","name":"安联的一角","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-708efb001ec970edaa78098a40f760ec_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-708efb001ec970edaa78098a40f760ec_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1f1a4f278ce4decc1a95d4d3fa069b78","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563299740","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546222829,"updated_time":1546222829,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你要是能证明这个猜想，别说保送了，清华、北大的教授任你挑。不过在这之前，恐怕你得先发现一些可以用于证明这个猜想的工具。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫猜想是数论这顶皇冠上的明珠。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559405093,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5aedf115769584ec22bc0ba48372a62a","url_token":"xie-wei-63-5-64","name":"退出在线生活","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8b0c91ec5a8a7809c6af29f1058fe8ad_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8b0c91ec5a8a7809c6af29f1058fe8ad_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5aedf115769584ec22bc0ba48372a62a","user_type":"people","headline":"世界只运行在相信他